quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,14,"Mubarwanye kugira ngo Allah abahane akoresheje amaboko yanyu, abakoze isoni ndetse namwe abahe intsinzi, kandi imitima y’abemera ayikize (agahinda)"
  9,15,"Ndetse anakure uburakari mu mitima yabo. Allah yakira ukwicuza k'uwo ashatse. Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  9,16,"Ese (mwe abemera) mwibwira ko muzarekwa (mutyo) Allah atagaragaje abaharaniye inzira ye muri mwe, ndetse bakaba bataragize inshuti magara ibindi bitari Allah n’intumwa ye ndetse n’abemera? Kandi Allah azi byimazeyo ibyo mukora"
  9,17,"Ntibikwiye ko ababangikanyamana bita ku misigiti ya Allah, kandi ubwabo bishinja ubuhakanyi. Abo ibikorwa byabo byabaye impfabusa, kandi bazaba mu muriro ubuziraherezo"
  9,18,"Mu by’ukuri, abita ku misigiti ya Allah ni babandi bemeye Allah n'umunsi w'imperuka, bagahozaho amasengesho, bagatanga amaturo ndetse ntibagire undi batinya utari Allah. Abo ni bo bayobotse (by’ukuri)"
  9,19,"Ese (igikorwa cyo) kwicira inyota abakora umutambagiro mutagatifu (Hijat) no kwita ku Musigiti Mutagatifu (Kabat), mubigereranya n’ibikorwa n’uwemeye Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka akanaharanira inzira ya Allah? Ntibashobora kureshya imbere ya Allah! Kandi Allah ntayobora ababangika nyamana"
  9,20,"Babandi bemeye, bakimukira (i Madina) ndetse bakanaharanira inzira ya Allah bakoresheje imitungo yabo na bo ubwabo, bafite urwego ruhambaye kwa Allah. Kandi abo ni bo batsinze"